* Every tiddler tagged with `$:/tags/SideBar` will appear in the ~Tiddlywiki sidebar
* The position in the sidebar can be determined using the `list-after` and `list-before` field
* If you want to change the text displayed in the sidebar, add the caption filed to that tiddler

